WEBVTT
NOTE Sworn demo video captions. Time-aligned to the shot list in plan.md.
NOTE Edit timings during final cut; word-level alignment from Whisper or Loom auto-caption.

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
In February 2024, a tribunal ruled an airline's chatbot

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
was a corporate statement.

00:08.000 --> 00:11.500
The airline argued it was a separate entity. The tribunal said no.

00:11.500 --> 00:15.000
AI mistakes are now uncapped corporate liability — and there is no audit trail.

00:15.000 --> 00:20.000
Sworn issues a cryptographic receipt under every AI agent reply.

00:20.000 --> 00:25.000
Anchored on 0G Chain. Persisted on 0G Storage.

00:25.000 --> 00:30.000
The URL is the receipt. Anyone can verify it.

00:30.000 --> 00:35.000
No login. No upload. No Sworn server in the trust path.

00:35.000 --> 00:42.000
Here's a customer service bot built on the Sworn SDK.

00:42.000 --> 00:50.000
I ask: what is your refund policy for damaged goods?

00:50.000 --> 00:58.000
Under every reply, a tiny receipt pill appears.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
The chatId on that pill is the dispute primitive.

01:05.000 --> 01:10.000
Clicking the receipt opens the verifier in your browser.

01:10.000 --> 01:18.000
Eleven cryptographic checks run locally against the real 0G Chain.

01:18.000 --> 01:25.000
Anchor exists. Storage retrievable. SHA-256 matches the on-chain root hash.

01:25.000 --> 01:32.000
Body parses, version 1. Prompt hash. Response hash.

01:32.000 --> 01:42.000
TEE signature valid against the snapshot public key. Provider not revoked.

01:42.000 --> 01:50.000
Model hash matches on-chain. All eleven of eleven.

01:50.000 --> 01:55.000
None of them trust us.

01:55.000 --> 02:02.000
The anchor lives on 0G Chain block 33,370,770.

02:02.000 --> 02:10.000
Five contracts back this. If Sworn disappears tomorrow,

02:10.000 --> 02:15.000
the receipt still verifies from the chain alone.

02:15.000 --> 02:22.000
Five contracts on Galileo testnet.

02:22.000 --> 02:30.000
ReceiptRegistry. RevocationRegistry. ReceiptDispute. CommitReveal. SwornReceiptInft.

02:30.000 --> 02:35.000
0G primitive depth 5 of 5.

02:35.000 --> 02:42.000
Drop-in TypeScript SDK. Read-only Python verifier.

02:42.000 --> 02:50.000
Browser extension that highlights any receipt on any page.

02:50.000 --> 02:55.000
Built for production AI teams, auditors, and insurance underwriters.

02:55.000 --> 03:00.000
yonkoo11.github.io/sworn
